snippet.title: Inmates - Gamescom Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Inmates on Steam: http://store.steampowered.com/app/634120/

Inmates is a story-driven, atmospheric psychological horror game. Featuring interactive exploration in a suffocating location, mind-bending puzzles and disturbing imagery. You wake up in a run-down prison cell and have no clue how you got there. You’ve convinced yourself this is all just a nightmare...

Looking for more information on Inmates? Check out the following channels:

Official website: http://www.inmatesgame.com
Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/inmates
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/inmatesgame
Twitter: http://twitter.com/inmatesgame / http://twitter.com/Iceberg_Int #InmatesGame
